    • putComment

      void putComment​(java.lang.String key, java.lang.String comment)
      Inserts the new comment for the specific item (key). If the key is null, the comment is used as a header comment for the whole section.
      Parameters:
      key - the name of the specific item
      comment - the associated comment to be inserted into the structure
